<!-- ══ TAB 4: TRADE-OFF & INSIGHTS ══ -->
<div class="panel" id="tab-insights">
  <!-- Trade-off Bubble Chart -->
  <div class="card-full">
    <div class="card-title">Trade-off Analysis — IE vs Text Quality Performance</div>
    <div class="chart-description">Bubble chart showing the trade-off between extraction quality (IE, x-axis) and text quality (y-axis). Bubble size represents Final Score. <strong>Quadrants:</strong> top-right = balanced (high both), top-left = quality-focused, bottom-right = extraction-focused, bottom-left = needs improvement.</div>
    <div style="position:relative;height:560px;width:100%;">
      <canvas id="tradeoffBubbleChart"></canvas>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-top:12px;padding:10px 14px;background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-sm);font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:12px;color:var(--muted2);line-height:1.6;display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:12px;">
      <span><strong style="color:var(--text);">Quadrant Guide</strong></span>
      <span style="color:var(--accent3);">↗ Top-right = Balanced</span>
      <span style="color:var(--accent2);">↖ Top-left = Quality-focused</span>
      <span style="color:var(--accent4);">↘ Bottom-right = Extraction-focused</span>
      <span style="color:var(--accent5);">↙ Bottom-left = Needs Improvement</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- FDR vs FNR Scatter -->
  {% if has_fdr_fnr %}
  <div class="card-full" style="margin-top:16px;">
    <div class="card-title">FDR vs FNR — Trade-off: Invented × Absent Vulnerabilities</div>
    <div class="chart-description">
      Each shape = one <strong>(LLM, baseline)</strong> pair · color = LLM · shape = baseline · large circle = LLM mean.
      <strong>FNR</strong> (X) = % real vulnerabilities missed = 1 − Recall.
      <strong>FDR</strong> (Y) = % detections that are false positives = 1 − Precision.
      Dashed lines connect each baseline point to the LLM mean — a wider "star" means more variance across ground-truth datasets.
      Adjust the sliders to set your tolerance thresholds — the <span style="color:#10b981;font-weight:600;">green zone</span> updates live.
    </div>

    <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;align-items:center;margin-bottom:0.6rem;margin-top:0.5rem;">
      <span class="ctrl-label">Baseline:</span>
      <div id="fdrBaselineBtns" style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:0;">
